# ==============================================================================
# HDRi environment maps (Team V Wave 1, 2026-05-05).
# Fetched from Polyhaven (CC0) by tools/fetch-hdri.ps1 — not committed
# because 1K .exr files are 0.5–1 MB each and regenerable on demand.
# The directory placeholder (.gitkeep) IS tracked.
# ==============================================================================
Voxelforge.Renderer/Assets/Hdri/*.exr

# ==============================================================================
# Logo exploration outputs (regenerated by assets/_gen_logos.py).
# Canonical deliverables — logo.svg, logo-dark.svg, logo-combo-{e,d1..d4}.svg,
# social-preview.svg, palette.svg — ARE tracked. The TPMS and gallery
# variants below are exploration-only and recreated on demand.
# ==============================================================================
assets/logo-tpms-*.svg
assets/logo-combo-a.svg
assets/logo-combo-b.svg
assets/logo-combo-c.svg
assets/logo-combo-d.svg
assets/logo-variants-gallery.svg
assets/logo-combos-gallery.svg

# ==============================================================================
# Generated design outputs (Save Design, batch-mode, multi-pillar StlExporter
# CLI). Patterns confirmed against actual writers:
#   *.rcd.json       — DesignPersistence.Save target (chamber Save Design dialog
#                      + batch-mode `{prefix}_design.rcd.json`).
#   *-design.json    — Multi-pillar StlExporter `--design <X-design.json>`
#                      convention (ntr-, marine-, ramjet-, resistojet-design.json)
#                      and BenchCalibrate `--write-back <design.json>`.
# Hot-fire and bench scripts emit these per run; nothing tracked matches.
# `out/` is already covered by `[Oo]ut/` above.
# ==============================================================================
*.rcd.json
*-design.json
